In [118]:
import folium

TX_Map = folium.Map(location=[TXNursing['Latitude'].mean(), TXNursing['Longitude'].mean()], zoom_start=6)
for Latitude, Longitude, InstitutionName, MainParentName in zip(TXNursing.Latitude, TXNursing.Longitude, TXNursing.InstitutionName, TXNursing.MainParentName):
    popup = f"{MainParentName}\n{InstitutionName}"
    folium.Marker(
        location=[Latitude, Longitude],
        popup=popup
    ).add_to(TX_Map)

#this map lets you isolate everything to 1 at a time
import folium
from ipywidgets import interact

TX_Map_Choice = folium.Map(location=[32.7767, -96.7970], zoom_start=6)

def add_markers(MainParentName):
    markers = folium.FeatureGroup(name="markers")
    filtered = TXNursing[TXNursing['MainParentName'] == MainParentName]
    for Latitude, Longitude, InstitutionName, MainParentName in zip(filtered.Latitude, filtered.Longitude, filtered.InstitutionName, filtered.MainParentName):
        folium.Marker(
            location=[Latitude, Longitude],
            popup=[MainParentName, InstitutionName],
        ).add_to(markers)
    markers.add_to(TX_Map_Choice)
    return TX_Map_Choice

interact(add_markers, MainParentName=TXNursing['MainParentName'].unique());
